snippet.title: LA Cops: The Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
LA COPS IS OUT NOW!
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/278810 
Xbox One: https://store.xbox.com/en-US/Xbox-One/Games/LA-Cops/a28ef191-6182-4bf1-ac77-4d4e94f0ad55

Follow LA Cops on twitter for more episodes: https://twitter.com/LACopsgame

LA Cops YouTube playlist: http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLjkadU1Gs-CFFmbQXDLkMdLBMXbO1stqa 

Subscribe to Team17's YouTube channel for more LA Cops, The Escapists, Worms and other great games! http://bit.ly/SubscribeT17 

LA Cops is developed by Modern Dream and published as part of the Team17 Indie Label. Check out the LA Cops website: http://www.la-cops.com/

Would you be a good LA Cop? Or a bad LA Cop? Let us know in the comments!
